Pre-Game Insights: Australia and England have had a tough battle with each other in the shortest format and have almost won an equal number of games. Aussies do have a challenge in the ongoing series due to the lack of some key members and England's home advantage.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Englishmen have been quite powerful at home in England vs Australia encounters. Out of 10 T20I games, England has won 6 and lost only 3.
Others: England and Australia are set to battle with each other in the 2nd T20I of the ongoing series. The ENG vs AUS 2nd T20I 2024 takes place on Friday, September 13.
The venue of ENG vs AUS 2nd T20I is Sophia Gardens in Cardiff, UK. Mitchell Marsh leads Australia while Phil Salt leads England.
